---
alwaysApply: true
---

All our go infrastructure runs in a docker container managed by scheduler-go service.

To run tests, you can use the following commands:

```bash
./services/scheduler-go/test-docker.sh
```

(use the --help flag to see all the options for our test runner)

```bash
./services/scheduler-go/test-docker.sh --help
```

To build the binary and dev servec, use the following command:

scripts/docker-compose build scheduler-go
